    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，PARSE之后需要分支吗？比如有效和无效数据的不同流向？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PARSE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，PARSE之后要分叉：Valid走ARB_READ去申请读权限，Invalid直接进ERROR状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PARSE",
        "ARB_READ",
        "ERROR",
        "Valid",
        "Invalid"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，ARB_READ获得Grant后进入READ，读完之后需要申请写权限吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ARB_READ",
        "READ",
        "Grant",
        "ARB_WRITE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是的，READ完成后进入ARB_WRITE申请写权限，Grant后执行WRITE，写完后进入CHAIN状态做链式处理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "READ",
        "ARB_WRITE",
        "WRITE",
